		}
		{
			dependencies: ["29EE940649C3AE38"]
			description: [
				"Finding coal can be difficult sometimes and you can't get charcoal easily. But there a other solutions! Sulfur or Sticky resin! You can use it as replacement for coal to craft torches!"
				""
				"You can get &lSticky Resin&r from chopping down &oGregtech Rubber Trees.&r"
				""
				"&lSulfur&r can be found in ores underground, but not far down, so you can do some minor digging or find a cave entrance."
			]
			id: "062CF3CD78A87B5B"
			rewards: [{
				count: 16
				id: "369E87243669AF5E"
				item: "minecraft:torch"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
				count: 4L
				id: "2B637A410F13CE22"
				item: { Count: 4, id: "minecraft:torch" }
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Sulfuric Torches"
			x: 2.1598639455782234d
			y: -0.9345238095238102d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["4EBBAB4B8A99D4A7"]
			dependency_requirement: "one_started"
			description: [
				"Most of machines while working generate pollution. Additionally explosions and torches can cause this too.  "
				""
				"There two types of pollution in the world: &lCarbon&r and &lSulfur&r."
				""
				"Pollution clouds will try to reach the atmosphere after appearing and then will continue to accumulate there. If there too much pollution in one area then you will get various debuffs."
			]
			icon: "adchimneys:large_brick_chimney"
			id: "1A45CB2CCDCAD4DB"
			subtitle: "Consequences of my inaction"
			tasks: [{
				id: "42F84E0C6C8D282D"
				title: "Pollution"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			x: 5.0d
			y: 2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A45CB2CCDCAD4DB"]
			description: [
				"Get generated by various machines and when you mine sulfur."
				""
				"Sulfur can contaminate water sources and eventually create podzol on any dirt related blocks. Even &ldestroy crops!&r So be careful with it!"
				""
				"if you will stand too long in sulfuric cloud you will get poison debuff."
			]
			icon: "adpother:sulfur"
			id: "0AA13BC0D2C48B13"
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "56595FBD91AA72B3"
