					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Sulfur"
			x: 6.0d
			y: 3.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1A45CB2CCDCAD4DB"]
			description: [
				"Carbon get generated when you mine coal and use torches to light your area. But the most source of carbon gonna be various machines. "
				""
				"If &ltoo much&r clouds will be stuck in one tight place they &ocan explode!&r And if you will stay in the cloud for too long you will get blindness debuff!"
				""
				"You can actually benefit from the carbon clouds if you will redirect them to places where your crops grow &lit will boost it growth!&r Sometimes you can see it even in your area: tall grass start appearing in vicinity of your factory that means there many carbon emissions."
			]
			icon: "adpother:carbon"
			id: "5D210874EE9C2BD3"
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "661A163BD2C102B0"
