					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Carbon"
			x: 6.0d
			y: 1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"5D210874EE9C2BD3"
				"0AA13BC0D2C48B13"
			]
			description: [
				"If you want to get rid of the pollution manually then you need two items: Vacuum bag and Vacuum tube. But at the same time &lto not get damaged by negative effects&r from pollution while collecting it you need &lRespirator&r. There three tiers of this items: iron, gold and diamond."
				""
				"Before you can collect any sulfur or carbon you need to put a filter in your Vacuum bag. Use anvil to apply filters: &oleaves for carbon&r and &owool for sulfur&r."
				""
				"After needed filter added wear bag in your chestplate slot and take tube in your main hand. Use it and now you will collect any pollution clouds in your bug. "
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "adpother:iron_vacuum_tube"
