		{
			dependencies: ["29EE940649C3AE38"]
			description: [
				"Ore veins added by Gregtech replace normal vanilla ore generation and aditionally spawn some other ores like tin, nickel, lead and etc."
				""
				"Ore veins very useful in getting massive amounts of resources and they are fairly common!"
				""
				"Find varoius dusts on the surface that indicate that ore vein underground. You can use your map to see where they are too! Just click a &lore icon&r in the low left corner. Additionaly you can see what type of ores are in the vein."
