			]
			description: [
				"Seared melter is first iteration of getting molten metals. Right now it can help get additional resource income. Simple and common ores can give additional 3 nuggets when using smeltery. Some metals require higher temperatures, so you need to upgrade to bigger smeltery later. You can't make alloys in small smeltery."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"To build melter put it on the Heater, then attach Faucet to it and put basin under for molten metals to flow. Fuel it with coal or any other solid fuel. Right-click Faucet to pour your liquids into the basin and create resource blocks. "
				""
				"You can automate process with hoppers and alike blocks. You can give Faucet a redstone signal (like putting lever near) to automatically pour out of Smeltery."
			]
