		{
			dependencies: ["34D049FD2BF84E84"]
			description: [
				"Ziplines are useful ways to go down a mountain or any other slopes. Put two zipline hooks at some distance and then click with rope at both of them to connect those points. You can even connect multiplie points to various hooks. Hold right click while on the rope to move along side it."
				""
				"Additionally if you put hooks at the same height level you can just use them as a way to cross pits and falls freely in both direction."
				""
				"Just keep in mind that using hooks will drain your stamina overtime, so don't forget to take a brakes."
				""
				"You can change colors of zipline rope by combining it with dyes in crafting grid. Its not limited by just minecraft standart colors."
				""
				"&lSee 'Transportation' tab for more things.&r"
