		{
			dependencies: ["34D049FD2BF84E84"]
			description: [
				"&lImmersive Geology&r add its own type of veins that can be used to get additional or alternative resources income. But unlike most of GregTech ones you need to crush them manually, compile and then use &oCrude Bloomery&r to get your ingots, at least before you will gate upgraded Blast Furnace."
				""
				"Geology ores have variants: poor, normal and rich. The better the gem the more crushed ore you will get."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Aside from using Geology normal ways of proccesing ores, with help of &lForge Hammer&r or &lMechanical Press&r you can automate the procces of getting dirty crushing ores. "
				""
				"After that with help of &lSteam Separator&r or simple mixer you can convert dirty crushed ores into ready to smelt ones which you can put into &lTinker's Smeltery&r."
			]
